---
title: Greek Turkey 'Gyros' with DIY Tzatziki and Chopped Salad
description: Creamy feta and fresh lemon add zip to tender roasted turkey. Load up your pita with turkey, tzatziki and some salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/greek-turkey-gyros-d530f135.jpg
